               <scopecontent id="aspace_fdd65ace54d6c984f0a7245f234a2ca9">
                  <head>Scope and Contents</head>
                  <p>Tells of dissatisfaction with the Russians as allies, especially on the march into Bohemia. Very cynical about the "virtuous set of Patriots" who shall bring on a new war.</p>
               </scopecontent>
            </c>
            <c id="ref38" level="file">
